---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
import packageJson from '../../package.json';

const VERSION = packageJson.version;
---

<Layout title="Release Notes — ScrabbleWordsFinder" description="Complete version changelog for ScrabbleWordsFinder.com. Track new features, bug fixes, and improvements to our free instant Scrabble word solver. Free." keywords="scrabble word finder changelog, release notes, version history, scrabble solver updates, new features">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-blue-400 hover:underline mb-6 inline-block">← Back to Solver</a>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Release Notes</h1>
      <a href="/tech-stack/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-1 rounded-lg text-gray-400 hover:text-purple-400 hover:bg-purple-900/20 transition-colors text-sm" title="Tech Stack"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.066 2.573c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573 1.066c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066-2.573c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg><span>Tech Stack</span></a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">Feature updates and improvements. Current version: <span class="font-mono text-blue-400">v{VERSION}</span></p>

    <div class="space-y-8">

      <!-- v1.19.3 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-blue-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.19.3 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 8, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Preconnect Hint — added preconnect to AdSense origin for faster ad loading on interaction</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Touch Targets Fixed — cookie consent buttons and diamond hunt gems now meet 48px minimum tap size</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Mobile Nav Icons — increased from 36px to 40px, added missing Cheat Sheets and Settings links</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Chat Mobile Spacing — reduced gap after avatar banner, added breathing room above it</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> SEO Keywords Sync — transferred updated keywords from seo_index DB to page files</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.19.2 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-cyan-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.19.2 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 8, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> PWA Complete — manifest, service worker, icons, and registration all in place; SWF installable as a standalone app with offline dictionary support</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Charset Header Fix — HTTP Content-Type now includes charset=utf-8 via middleware for all HTML responses</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Organization Schema (GEO) — JSON-LD Organization schema on homepage for LLM and AI search engine discoverability</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> H1 Tags — added to all 149 pages that were missing them, with keyword-enriched subtitles</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> SEO Tag Audit Panel — new admin/seo section showing presence, coverage, avg/min/max lengths and stipulated ranges for all SEO elements</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> FAQPage Schema — added to avatar-collage and WOTD archive (now 100% coverage)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> H2 Headings — added semantic headings to 5 app pages for accessibility and SEO (now 100% coverage)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> SEO Index Sync — new script (sync-seo-index.mjs) extracts metadata from all 1038 .astro files into the seo_index DB</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.19.1 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.19.1 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 6, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Badge UI Overhaul — gold/silver metallic gradients, embossed shadows, Celtic corner ornaments, and coloured glow effects on all badge cards</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Diamond Requirements Visible — each badge now displays the number of diamonds needed to unlock it</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> "Completed" Rubber Stamp — achieved badges show a tilted stamp on the card corner for instant visual recognition</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Badge LocalStorage Save — save achieved badges locally for faster loading and offline badge display</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Badge Glow — consistent multi-colour drop-shadow glow that follows the shield artwork shape on all badges</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex Coaching Token Fix — AI coaching report token limit increased from 300-450 to 1000, eliminating truncated PDFs</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex Challenge Quality — coaching prompts updated to prevent impossible challenges like "solve in 0 attempts"</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Performance — click counter polling reduced from 2s to 30s, requestIdleCallback for non-critical fetches</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Vite Cache Fix Tool — python3 script to auto-fix stale SSR dependency cache errors</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.19.0 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-emerald-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.19.0 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 5, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Core Web Vitals Fix — 150 blog pages prerendered to static HTML, reducing Worker bundle from 50MB to 15MB and TTFB from 1.4s to ~100ms</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Admin Site Status Page — combined Telemetry + Live Sessions + Latest Clicks dashboard at /admin/site-status/</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Admin Dashboard Widgets — Live Sessions and Latest Clicks panels added inline to the Site Status section on /admin/</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Email Campaigns — bounced/prospective/no-response status tracking with colour-coded rows, pin feature, email variant selector, batch regrouping (250/batch)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Daily Anagram Cache Fix — date-keyed localStorage prevents stale puzzles bleeding between days</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Diamond Earned Modal — proper celebration popup when all daily stars collected</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Chat Skill Level Starters — beginner/intermediate/advanced coaching prompts added to /chat/</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Coaching PDF Fix — progression trend section now handles all coach types (rack uses points, quiz/anagram use percentages)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> AI Live Test Suite — 7 new Playwright tests covering solver flow, coaching reports, leaderboard, WOTD, quiz, and daily rack</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Bounced Email Processor — Python tool to parse bounce/reply .zip files and update campaign_leads status</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> SEO Index Live Sync — 1,044 pages tracked with crawl dates from Google Search Console</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Smoke Test Fixes — structured data assertion and sensitive data regex corrected</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.18.1 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-teal-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.18.1 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 4, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Cheat Sheet Cross-Links — icon navigation bar added to SOWPODS and TWL cheat sheets for easy switching between dictionaries</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> SEO Index Sync Links — new "Sync Links" button re-scans all pages and updates internal link counts, H2s, word counts, and schema presence</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> SEO Sync to Pages — reworked to compare DB edits with live pages, log field-level changes to sync log with full values and character counters</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Incremental Sync — Sync to Pages now only processes pages updated since last sync, preventing server overload on large sites</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Crawled Column Sortable — the Crawled column in the SEO index tracker is now clickable and sortable</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Search Relevance — SEO index search now prioritises shorter URL matches first (exact pages appear before blog posts containing the term)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Welcome Banner — complete border with rounded corners for avatar welcome strip</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Bug fix — corrected corrupted meta description in average-winning-score blog post</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.18.0 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-sky-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.18.0 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 4, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Ask Lex Integration — "Learn with Lex AI" button now passes rack tiles directly to the chat page for contextual coaching</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Chat UI — larger voice input button and "Ask Lex" send button for better usability</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Blog Batch 3 Progress — specialty word list pages expanded from stubs to full content (180+ lines with visual treatment)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Admin Clicks Sound Picker — choose between Bell Gong, Bugle Call, Fog Horn, or Toon Horn for click alerts (persists between sessions)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Blog fixes — layout migrations, BlogCrossLinks improvements, new long-form strategy articles</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> 10 new long-form blog posts — strategy masterclass, tile management, board geometry, opponent reading, endgame tactics, and more</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Backend improvements — admin tooling updates and internal infrastructure enhancements</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.17.0 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-rose-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.17.0 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 2, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Structured Coaching Reports — Lex coaching output restructured into clear sections: Grade, Strengths, Needs Work, Trends, Timing, Prediction, Words to Learn, and Challenge</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Coaching PDF Export — generate and download professional PDF reports from any coaching session (Quiz, Rack, Anagram, CaB)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Saved Reports Panel — save up to 5 coaching PDFs locally with view and delete controls (appears in chat sidebar)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Predictive Coaching — data-driven improvement estimates based on your play patterns and historical trends</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex's Challenge — personalised goal-setting section added to every coaching report to drive improvement</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Memory Retention — missed words with definitions included in coaching reports for vocabulary building</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Banned Filler Phrases — Lex now avoids vague coaching language, producing more concise and actionable advice</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Shared prompt builder — DRY refactor using <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">buildQuizCoachPrompt</code> across chat and API endpoints</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-rose-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Test suite — 9 new jsPDF/coaching-pdf tests plus updated coaching API specs</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.16.0 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-teal-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.16.0 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 2, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Player Avatars — unique animal avatars assigned automatically to every player, viewable across the site</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Welcome Banner — personalised greeting bar above the header showing your avatar and display name</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Avatar Swap — swap your avatar and name anytime from the dedicated page</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Avatar Collage — visual gallery of all 25 animal avatars</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Leaderboard — site-wide rankings at <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">/leaderboard/</code> showing top players by stars and diamonds</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> 60-Second Challenge leaderboard — submit your score after timed rounds and compete for top spots</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Daily Duel panel — new daily competitive word challenge on the Activities page</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> MyBag avatar display — your avatar now appears on your personal bag page</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Settings avatar preview — see and manage your avatar from the settings page</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Admin avatars dashboard — management page for avatar distribution and usage stats</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Blog — new "How to Play Scrabble" video guides post with embedded tutorials</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Chat improvements — Memory WordBench modal, keyword-triggered 3-letter word helpers, and Learn with Lex links</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> UI polish — inline welcome info button, solver quick-link refinements, StarBar layout updates</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Test suite — 40+ new spec files covering avatars, leaderboard, daily duel, welcome banner, chat, and blog features</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.15.0 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-amber-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">v1.15.0 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-normal ml-2">July 2, 2026</span></h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex Quick-Reference Word Lists — system prompt now includes curated two-letter words, top 3-letter words, highest-scoring words by length, Q-without-U words, and rare letter power words with scores</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> EV Scoring Engine — new Expected Value rack quality scorer (0-100) analysing vowel/consonant ratio, power tiles, bingo stems, and duplicates</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex Query Classifier — intelligent routing categorises user messages (rack, strategy, word-list, coaching) for optimised responses</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Coaching Prompts library — dedicated prompt templates for Quiz, CaB, Rack, and Anagram coaching sessions</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Training Modes module — foundation for Bingo Trainer, Hook Quiz, Tile Countdown, and Rack Leave Drill</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Coaching renderers — external <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">/js/coaching-renderers.js</code> for quiz, rack, and anagram coaching data visualisation</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> New APIs — <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">/api/lex-cab-coach/</code>, <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">/api/lex-rack-coach/</code>, <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">/api/lex-training/</code></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Activity panels enhanced — CaB, Daily Anagram, and Daily Rack panels updated with Lex coaching integration</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Blog — 50+ thematic word posts (yoga, witchcraft, woodwork, winter, summer, opera, painting, and more)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex Dojo mode — interactive training modes accessible from the chat page</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Test suite — 20+ new spec files covering EV scoring, chat streaming, coaching endpoints, dojo modes, and word-list queries</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.14.4 -->
      <article class="border-l-2 border-purple-500 pl-4">
