        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Lex AI Solver modal — "Ask Lex AI" button on the solver now opens an inline modal with rack input, word finding, and free-form Scrabble chat</li>
