          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> WOTD memorised — checkbox to mark words as memorised with persistent local tracking</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Chat context routing — <code class="text-xs bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded">/chat/?context=rack</code> auto-submits personalised Daily Rack coaching request with full play history</li>
