          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">✦</span> Test suite — 25+ new spec files covering Lex solver modal, coaching links, quiz timing stats, anagram coach, DRC context, WOTD languages and memorised features</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- v1.14.3 -->
